headline: EMMY® AWARD-WINNING ACTOR ERIC STONESTREET SHOWCASES HOW TRAVELERS CAN 'EXPERIENCE MORE AT SEA™' WITH NORWEGIAN CRUISE LINE IN ITS NEW AD CAMPAIGN
summary: Norwegian Cruise Line® (NCL), the innovator in global cruise travel, today announced the two-time Emmy®-Award-winning actor, Eric Stonestreet, as the Company's new brand ambassador and star of its newest advertising campaign, "Experience More."

headline: How MSC Cruises Built Its Own Private Island Retreat From a Dredging Site
summary: Cruise lines are pouring increasing sums into private islands that give them more control over the guest experience. Here’s how MSC spent $500 million transforming a dredging site into a destination.
